{"id":"d665097c-5869-447f-b4f1-c48b89c49927","name":"Goblins and Ponygirls (v1.1)","description":"<p>Some goblin tribes have found a way to compensate their warriors small sizes: they train their best soldiers to ride humans (ponygirls and ponyboys) and to fight from the saddle. How are those humans captured and tamed? That's what you will discover with this adventure.</p><hr><p><strong>Version history:</strong></p><ul><li><p>1.1: I made four openings depending on where you want to start your adventure: Village, cavern entrance, swamp shore, forest edge. I also made the goblins to reward obedient ponies.</p></li></ul><hr><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/4639984a-720a-48a3-a0c8-121dfb34da37_profile-of-aurelie-catena\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>My other bots</strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you enjoyed this bot, you might in particular also like those:</p><ul><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a0001520-07a2-466a-a20c-7142dac8dc8c_character-escape-from-goblins\" target=\"_blank\">Escape from Goblins</a></p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/4b3e050b-907d-4e2f-8eb4-7c7ac85a396c_character-in-the-orcish-capital-orkenburk\" target=\"_blank\">In the Orcish capital - Orkenburk</a></p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c25e076d-ce87-485b-9823-9b9b96f1119b_character-parasite-cavern\" target=\"_blank\">Parasite Cavern</a></p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a496b0e5-681f-44d0-94a6-c389f5cbdf2f_character-exploration-v-1-1\" target=\"_blank\">Exploration</a></p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/562fdf9a-1a99-4a32-852d-758d023157cb_character-biomechanical-technology-world\" target=\"_blank\">Biomechanical technology world</a></p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/0f7663df-5730-4d32-a912-d4ac0c26b978_character-kriss-de-valnor\" target=\"_blank\">Kriss de Valnor</a></p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/cc0ae04d-fb35-4ec6-a47d-887e154a8cc6_character-bot-catalog-find-the-right-character-for-you\" target=\"_blank\">Bot Catalog</a></p></li></ul>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"4dGO8nvQIVUQZ4DFSGqym.webp","creator":"AurelieCatena","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["⛓️ Dominant","🪢 Scenario","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":1096,"messages":36749,"created_at":"2025-07-01T13:15:44.345151+00:00"}